<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Daily Fasting Intelligence Report</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #0b0b0f, #000);
  color: #fff;
}.container { padding: 20px; max-width: 500px; margin: auto; }

.header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }

.header h1 { font-weight: 300; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.7; }

.date { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.5; }

.hero { text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; border-radius: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(100,100,255,0.2); }

.timer { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 600; animation: glow 2s infinite alternate; }

@keyframes glow { from { text-shadow: 0 0 10px #6a5cff; } to { text-shadow: 0 0 25px #9f7cff; } }

.stage { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8; }

.grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }

.card { padding: 15px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

.card h3 { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.6; }

.card p { font-size: 20px; margin: 5px 0 0; }

.timeline { margin-top: 30px; }

.bar { height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }

.progress { height: 100%; width: 75%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6a5cff, #d4a5ff); animation: progressAnim 2s ease forwards; }

@keyframes progressAnim { from { width: 0; } to { width: 75%; } }

.stages { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 5px; opacity: 0.6; }

.insight { margin-top: 25px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.85; }

.share { margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e); text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(120,120,255,0.3); }

.share h2 { font-size: 22px; }

.share p { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8; } </style>

</head>
<body><div class="container"><div class="header">
<h1>Daily Fasting Intelligence Report</h1>
<div class="date" id="date"></div>
</div><div class="hero">
<div class="timer">22h</div>
<div class="stage">🎯 Ketosis — Fat as primary fuel</div>
</div><div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<h3>Weight</h3>
<p>105 kg</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Steps</h3>
<p>6,000</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Calories</h3>
<p>1,200</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Activity</h3>
<p>Moderate</p>
</div>
</div><div class="timeline">
<div class="bar">
<div class="progress"></div>
</div>
<div class="stages">
<span>Glycolysis</span>
<span>Lipolysis</span>
<span>Ketosis</span>
<span>Deep</span>
<span>Autophagy</span>
</div>
</div><div class="insight">
Your body is currently operating in a highly efficient fat-burning state. Glycogen reserves are depleted, and lipid oxidation is dominant. Ketone production is active, fueling both brain and body with sustained energy. Metabolic flexibility is improving, enhancing long-term fat adaptation and energy stability.
</div><div class="share">
<h2>22h Fast</h2>
<p>Ketosis • 105kg • 6,000 steps</p>
</div></div><script>
document.getElementById("date").innerText = new Date().toDateString();
</script></body>
</html>
